    <item>
      <title>Daily Security News from @trustpath - Apr 26, 2017</title>
      <link>//crypt0.net/daily/daily-trust-news-2017-04-26/</link>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Apr 2017 18:05:01 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>//crypt0.net/daily/daily-trust-news-2017-04-26/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Daily Security news from &lt;a href=&#34;http://twitter.com/trustpath&#34;&gt;@trustpath&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Carbon Black asks: So what exactly is threat hunting?&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Quite simply, threat hunting is the pursuit of abnormal activity on servers and endpoints that may be signs of compromise, intrusion or exfiltration of &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;https://securitybrief.com.au/story/carbon-black-asks-so-what-exactly-threat-hunting/&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;https://securitybrief.com.au/story/carbon-black-asks-so-what-exactly-threat-hunting/&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Hacker breaches personal data on state website&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Bowles said state agencies are increasingly being affected by data breaches. &amp;ldquo;It&amp;rsquo;s important the state do its due diligence to ensure those third party &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://katv.com/news/local/hacker-breaches-personal-data-on-state-website&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://katv.com/news/local/hacker-breaches-personal-data-on-state-website&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Beazley sees new phishing threats emerge&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;During the first quarter of 2017, Beazley&amp;rsquo;s BBR Services division managed 641 data breaches on behalf of clients, compared to 462 breaches during &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://globenewswire.com/news-release/2017/04/25/970887/0/en/Beazley-sees-new-phishing-threats-emerge.html&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://globenewswire.com/news-release/2017/04/25/970887/0/en/Beazley-sees-new-phishing-threats-emerge.html&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;The Hunter Strikes Back: The SANS 2017 Threat Hunting Survey&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;SANS 2017 Threat Hunting Survey show that, for many organizations, hunting &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.sans.org/reading-room/whitepapers/analyst/hunter-strikes-back-2017-threat-hunting-survey_37760&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;https://www.sans.org/reading-room/whitepapers/analyst/hunter-strikes-back-2017-threat-hunting-survey_37760&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;CrowdStrike Expands into Latin America, Opens Office in Mexico City&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;CrowdStrike Inc., the leader in cloud-delivered next-generation endpoint protection, today announced the launch of its operations in Latin America to &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://finance.yahoo.com/news/crowdstrike-expands-latin-america-opens-130000084.html&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://finance.yahoo.com/news/crowdstrike-expands-latin-america-opens-130000084.html&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;SS8 Networks Achieves Record Revenues and Profitability&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;intelligence, compliance and breach detection solutions among enterprises, critical &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.ss8.com/ss8-networks-achieves-record-revenues-profitability/&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;https://www.ss8.com/ss8-networks-achieves-record-revenues-profitability/&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;1.1 billion identities exposed in data breaches in 2016, says Symantec&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Livemint New Delhi: In the last eight years, more than 7.1 billion identities have been exposed in data breaches globally, which is almost the equivalent of one &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.livemint.com/Industry/mCSJiFfZrxk8USJ0Rxh8lI/11-billion-identities-exposed-in-data-breaches-in-2016-say.html&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.livemint.com/Industry/mCSJiFfZrxk8USJ0Rxh8lI/11-billion-identities-exposed-in-data-breaches-in-2016-say.html&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;How to deal with data breaches and fraud&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Greenville, N.C. (WNCT)  We continue our coverage on how to battle credit card fraud and data breaches. In our area we have seen incidents where &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://wnct.com/2017/04/26/how-to-deal-with-data-breaches-and-fraud/&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://wnct.com/2017/04/26/how-to-deal-with-data-breaches-and-fraud/&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Index Engines and FTI Consulting Partner to Deliver Enterprise-Scale Data&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Benzinga &amp;ldquo;As data breaches and data privacy regulations dominate the news, companies can&amp;rsquo;t afford the risk of letting their networks and legacy tape &amp;lsquo;dark data&amp;rsquo; &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.benzinga.com/pressreleases/17/04/p9347107/index-engines-and-fti-consulting-partner-to-deliver-enterprise-scale-da&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;https://www.benzinga.com/pressreleases/17/04/p9347107/index-engines-and-fti-consulting-partner-to-deliver-enterprise-scale-da&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Centrify Warns Password Vaults Alone Not Enough to Stop Data Breaches&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Data breaches are happening at an alarming rate and to stop them Centrify is taking a unique approach to controlling privileged access in the hybrid &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://finance.yahoo.com/news/centrify-warns-password-vaults-alone-120000498.html&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://finance.yahoo.com/news/centrify-warns-password-vaults-alone-120000498.html&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Hotels shown to be susceptible to cybercrime&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As for the hotel industry, Hilton, Hyatt and Starwood have reported data breaches at hotels since 2015. Brian Krebs, a Virginia-based writer of the &amp;hellip;  &lt;a href=&#34;http://www.travelweekly.com/Travel-News/Hotel-News/Hotels-shown-to-be-susceptible-to-cybercrime&#34; onclick=&#34;trackOutboundLink(&#39;http://www.travelweekly.com/Travel-News/Hotel-News/Hotels-shown-to-be-susceptible-to-cybercrime&#39;); return false;&#34;&gt;more&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;h3&gt;Healthcare data breaches &amp;lsquo;most likely&amp;rsquo; to occur in pharmacy&lt;/h3&gt;
